10 An act relating to amending a death certificate to reflect gender identity
11 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
12 Sec. 1. 18 V.S.A. § 5202a is amended to read:
13 § 5202a. CORRECTION, COMPLETION, OR AMENDMENT OF DEATH
14 CERTIFICATE
15 * * *
16 (g) Gender identity. The State Registrar may correct or amend a death
17 certificate to reflect the deceased person’s gender identity at the time of death,
18 upon application by:
19 (1) the certifying licensed health care professional, medical examiner,
20 hospital, or nursing home; or
